Enum nvinfer.UnaryOperation

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<nvinfer.UnaryOperation>
      • org.bytedeco.tensorrt.global.nvinfer.UnaryOperation
  • All Implemented Interfaces:

    Enclosing class:
    nvinfer

    @Namespace(value="nvinfer1")
public static enum nvinfer.UnaryOperation
extends Enum<nvinfer.UnaryOperation>
    \enum UnaryOperation \brief Enumerates the unary operations that may be performed by a Unary layer. Operations kNOT must have inputs of DataType::kBOOL. Operation kSIGN and kABS must have inputs of floating-point type, DataType::kINT8, DataType::kINT32 or DataType::kINT64. Operation kISINF must have inputs of floating-point type. All other operations must have inputs of floating-point type.
    See Also:
    IUnaryLayer
